Your Lordship,

Her Holiness pleased to propose a Concordat (a diplomatic agreement with the church) with the following terms:

The Church would like:
- For Your Lordship to profess the Venilian faith
- A church in Your Lordship's territory
- Legislative support should it be needed

The Church is prepared to offer:
- The title of Archbishop in the Archdiocese of Auredea
- Use of a papal apartment
- The papal style of His Excellency
- Ecclesiastical support with your motions in Parliament, including the Warp Magic Act 2025.

Please send your response to PONMAX via post. If you would like to alter any terms, make an alternative proposition, request a different title, etc. Her Holiness is open to discussion.
